{"tid":492561,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"驅逐愛國者","createTime":"2017-12-07T15:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T18:27:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"249e9a2567da3e1ac18e34640ee3776fa652083f","tid":492561,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20171207/20236682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171207%2F20236682&d=EMxhgrve49RE%2BatvF59NiL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=69726961\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171207%2F20236682&h=f21fea85\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20171207/20236682</a><br />\n<br />\n驅逐愛國者<br />\n<br />\n17,194<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20171207/large/1512549425_1596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20171207%2Flarge%2F1512549425_1596.jpg&h=367a7f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n北京驅逐800萬「低端人口」，其中一個被驅逐者，據悉是愛國小生意人。這個不知甚麼地方的外省民工，在北京開小店賣滷水蛋，生意一度紅火。店主亦囂張地在鋪頭懸掛一張手寫字通告，列出日本人、韓國人等若干國籍的顧客不受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n滷水蛋檔主寫那張通告的時候心中必定充滿自豪，相信自己是盛世強國站起來了的中國人，是當家做主的中國人，是他交了租納了稅的那個小攤檔的主人，所以他有權選擇歡迎甚麼客人、拒絕甚麼客人。他想必可以很自豪地對他的兒子說，「你看！做一個中國人多好！有兩隻手、肯勞動就一定能致富。小日本、小韓國還不是要看咱們中國臉色？連美國也怕咱們中國！中國就是強！」<br />\n他做夢也沒想過，有一天，他突然被驅逐，他的那個「當家做主」的小鋪頭也在他眼皮底下被鏟走。不需要任何理由，只因為他是「低端人口」。某一些人掌握着將中國人劃分為低端及高端的話語權、鑒定權。<br />\n<br />\n中國那麼大，可是哪兒是他的容身之所？<br />\n<br />\n他的妻兒跟在他身後，他卻找不到方向。他是那麼熱愛他腳下的這一片地，但是有人在他頭上蓋了一個印，宣告他無權站在那片地上。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=EMxhgrve49RE%2BatvF59NiL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=88cbb922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n講　價 (曾志豪)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n臺灣漢子李明哲 (古德明)"},{"pid":"80bceb1824b4e5e758634963be364a0f786a3b7d","tid":492561,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 習大 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a703406a05c94304be26fd01f245fd180b281767","tid":492561,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T18:27:09.000Z","msg":"「你看！做一個中國人多好！有兩隻手、肯勞動就一定能致富。小日本、小韓國還不是要看咱們中國臉色？連美國也怕咱們中國！中國就是強！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}